Title: EpiTxDb RMBase v2.0 for Saccharomyces cerevisiae sacCer3
Description: Information from the RMBase v2.0 was downloaded and imported as EpiTxDb database. All valid modification types for Saccharomyces cerevisiae/sacCer3 were used and checked the nucleotide sequence.

Title: EpiTxDb tRNAdb for Saccharomyces cerevisiae sacCer3
Description: tRNAdb entries for RNA database were imported using tRNAdbImport and the modification information extracted. tRNA sequences were matched against transcripts, results combined and stored as EpiTxDb database.
